  <brief_title>Study of Glucarpidase (CPG2) for the Management of Patients With Delayed Methotrexate Clearance</brief_title>
  <official_title>Study of Recombinant Carboxypeptidase G2 (CPG2) for the Management of Patients With Delayed Methotrexate (MTX) Clearance or Intrathecal MTX Overdosage</official_title>
  <sponsors>
