  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the safety and efficacy of glucarpidase in patients with impaired methotrexate
      (MTX) clearance owing to MTX-induced renal failure following high-dose MTX therapy, or with
      intrathecal MTX overdose.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
